Just download hamachi, then check the ip in hamachi (yours). Run your server and client, fill in the Hamachi ip in the client and login. Your friends and other visitors can open the client, fill in YOUR Hamachi ip and play!

Good luck;)

NOTE: THE VISITORS MUST BE IN YOUR HAMACHI CHANNEL FOR THIS TO WORK!!
